Answer-4
In html we have two types of tag
a.paired tag-->consist opening and closing tag
    ex-<html>(opening tag)</html>(closing tag)
        <p>(opening tag)</p>(closing tag) etc
b.self closing tag--> consist one tag only
    ex-<br>
        <hr>etc
tags are the structural component of a code it contains angular brackets
elements are defined by a start tag content and close tag

Answer-5
DOCTYPE is the first line in every html code,which tells the browser which version of html used in the code